Sentencas: A single cell solid oxide electrolyte direct carbon fuel cell with two biomass carbon fuel performances is presented in this article.
Titulo: Solid Oxide Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Electrochemical Performance Using Wheat and Spruce Carbon Fuels

Sentencas: The performances of the wheat carbon fuel are better than those of the spruce fuel.
Titulo: Solid Oxide Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Electrochemical Performance Using Wheat and Spruce Carbon Fuels

Sentencas: At 800 degrees C the open circuit voltage of wheat fuel (1.18 V) was slightly higher than spruce (1.16 V).
Titulo: Solid Oxide Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Electrochemical Performance Using Wheat and Spruce Carbon Fuels

Sentencas: The peak power density recorded for wheat fuel was 66.92 mW/cm(2) while spruce fuel was lower at 57.40 mW/cm(2).
Titulo: Solid Oxide Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Electrochemical Performance Using Wheat and Spruce Carbon Fuels

Sentencas: On the contrast spruce fuel (156.20 mA/cm(2)) gave a maximum current density with wheat fuel lower at 138.52 mA/cm(2).
Titulo: Solid Oxide Direct Carbon Fuel Cell Electrochemical Performance Using Wheat and Spruce Carbon Fuels
